{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two">

      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">
        Do you?
      </h1>

      <h2>
          <a href="/mental-health/depression">
          Feel a loss of interest or pleasure, general sadness, feelings of guilt or low self-worth, difficulty falling asleep, eating pattern changes, exhaustion and a lack of concentration?
          </a>
      </h2>
<br>
      <h2>
            <a href="/mental-health/anxiety">
              Feel restless, a sense of dread, feel constantly "on edge", have difficulty concentrating, are irritable?
              Regularly experience dry mouth, feeling sick/stomach ache, trembling/shaking?
              </a>
      </h2>

      <h2>
      <a href="/bipolar-disorder">
      Feel your mood can swing from one extreme to another with episodes/feeling lasting a number of weeks?
      Episodes can include overwhelming feelings of worthlessness or extreme happiness with elevated energy, ambitious plans and ideas.
      </a>
      </h2>

      <h2>
      <a href="/dementia">
      Do you experience any change in behaviour or thoughts, such as hallucinations or delusions?
      Feel a withdrawal or lack of function that you would not usually expect to feel? Do you feel emotionless / flat?
      </a>
      </h2>

      <h2>
      <a href="/schizophrenia">
      Struggle to remember past events much more than recent ones?
      Feel anxious, depressed or angry about memory loss, or feeling confused, even when in a familiar environment?
      </a>
      </h2>
  </div>

</div>

{% endblock %}